	(text "Oscillator Load Capacitance Calculations\nC_L = (C_L_Cry - C_Str) * 2\n	= (10pF - 5pF) * 2\n	= 10pF\n\nNote: Crystal => X322516MMB4SI\n\nResources Used:\n	1. STM32F103x8 Datasheet\n	2. AMS1117-3.3 Datasheet\n	3. ST Application Note AN4879 \n	Introduction to USB hardware and \n	PCB guidelines using STM32 MCUs\n	4. ST Application Note AN2867\n	Guidelines for oscillator design on \n	STM8AF/AL/S and STM32 MCUs/MPUs"
